Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.43,0:00:34.33,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1100,900)}{\pos(190,278)}伴我同行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.37,0:01:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"克利斯多佛詹伯斯律师  在餐厅劝架不成反遭杀害"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.20,0:01:36.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次见到死尸  是在刚过我12岁后不久\N{\fs14}I was twelve, going on thirteen, the first time I saw a dead human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情发生于1959年的夏季\N{\fs14}It happened in the summer of 1 959.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.31,0:01:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是好久以前了\N{\fs14}A long time ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.28,0:01:46.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但对我而言却恍如昨日\N{\fs14}but only if you measure in terms of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.05,0:01:55.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时我家住在奥勒冈州  一个叫岩堡的小镇\N{\fs14}I was living in a small town in Oregon called Castle Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:59.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,镇上只有一千两百余居民  但对我而言那已是整个世界\N{\fs14}There were only 1,28 1 people, but to me it was the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.86,0:02:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位  又到了"大老板"鲍伯·克米尔时间  今天早晨波特兰阳光普照\N{\fs14}Hey, it's the bossman Bob Cormier here. It's a beautiful Friday in Portland.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.63,0:02:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气温是华氏90度而且还在上升\N{\fs14}It's 90 KLAM degrees and getting hotter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.70,0:02:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着是排行榜上另一首当红单曲  鲍比戴的《摇滚罗宾》\N{\fs14}Up the ladder with another platter. It's Bobby Day with Rockin' Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.11,0:02:11.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酷毙了\N{\fs14}It's boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.43,0:02:31.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猜个谜  你如何看出法国人来过你家后院?\N{\fs14}How do you know a Frenchman's been in your backyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.56,0:02:33.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简单  因为自己是法国人\N{\fs14}I'm French, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.10,0:02:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案是你家垃圾桶被掏空  而狗被搞大了肚子\N{\fs14}Your garbage cans are empty and your dog's pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.00,0:02:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是我的答案比较好\N{\fs14}Didn't I just say I was French?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.04,0:02:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看牌\N{\fs14}I knock.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.10,0:02:41.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶\N{\fs14}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.77,0:02:43.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,29点\N{\fs14}Twenty-nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.07,0:02:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-22点  -又完蛋了\N{\fs14}- Twenty-two. - Piss up a rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.28,0:02:52.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈帝又完了  戈帝又被扫地出门了\N{\fs14}Gordie's out. Old Gordie just bit the bag and stepped out the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.48,0:02:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了  老兄\N{\fs14}Come on, man. Deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.05,0:02:58.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰迪·杜强是我们这伙儿人里  最神经的家伙\N{\fs14}Teddy Duchamp was the craziest guy we hung around with.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他命不太好\N{\fs14}He didn't have much of a chance in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.19,0:03:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸喜怒无常  脾气暴躁\N{\fs14}His dad was given to fits of rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.56,0:03:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一次他把泰迪的耳朵  扯到火炉边\N{\fs14}One time he held Teddy's ear to a stove...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.86,0:03:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几乎要烧掉了\N{\fs14}and almost burned it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.03,0:03:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看牌\N{\fs14}I knock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:12.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个四眼狗屎\N{\fs14}You four-eyed pile of shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗屎何止四眼  千眼都不只\N{\fs14}The pile of shit has a thousand eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.07,0:03:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛?\N{\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.14,0:03:20.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么好笑?  我30点  你呢?\N{\fs14}What's so funny? I've got 30. What have you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.64,0:03:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-16点  -再笑啊  笑死活该\N{\fs14}- Sixteen. - Go ahead. Keep laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.71,0:03:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是我的手下败将\N{\fs14}You're down to your ride, pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克利斯·詹伯斯是我们的帮主  也是我最好的朋友\N{\fs14}Chris Chambers was the leader of our gang, and my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.99,0:03:33.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的家庭不大幸福  大家都认定他以后会是个恶棍\N{\fs14}He came from a bad family, and everyone just knew he'd turn out bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.39,0:03:35.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克利斯自己也有同感\N{\fs14}Including Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:38.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是我们的敲门暗号\N{\fs14}That's not the secret knock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把敲门暗号给忘了  快让我进来\N{\fs14}I forget the secret knock. Let me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.63,0:03:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维恩\N{\fs14}Vern.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.40,0:03:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  你们这些家伙快开门\N{\fs14}Come on, you guys. Open up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着  你们绝对不会相信\N{\fs14}Oh, man, you guys are not gonna believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这太酷了\N{\fs14}This is so boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:52.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们听了就知道\N{\fs14}Oh, man, wait'll you hear this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.34,0:03:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们绝不会相信  这事令人难以置信\N{\fs14}You won't believe it. It's unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先让我喘口气  我从家里一直跑到这儿\N{\fs14}Let me catch my breath. I ran all the way from my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:04:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跑一路跑到家\N{\fs14}I ran all the way home
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.02,0:04:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少来了  你们听我说  这真的很酷\N{\fs14}Come on, you guys. This is boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:05.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只为了向你说声抱歉\N{\fs14}Just to say I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.52,0:04:08.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  不想听就算了\N{\fs14}Okay, forget it. I don't have to tell you nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.73,0:04:10.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄弟们  别唱了  究竟是什么大消息?\N{\fs14}Hold on, you guys. What is it, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.03,0:04:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保证轰动  你们绝不敢相信  不盖你们\N{\fs14}You won't believe this. Sincerely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.36,0:04:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一路跑到家\N{\fs14}I ran all the way home
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.37,0:04:16.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些浑球\N{\fs14}Screw you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.87,0:04:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不想听算了  -究竟是什么事?\N{\fs14}- Forget it. - What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们今晚可不可以在外过夜?\N{\fs14}Can you guys camp out tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.10,0:04:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说如果告诉你们老爸  今晚要在我家露营?\N{\fs14}If you tell your folks you're gonna tent out in my field?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.74,0:04:25.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想应该没问题\N{\fs14}Yeah, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.84,0:04:29.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是我爸最近脾气不太好  他最近喝酒喝的很凶\N{\fs14}Except my dad's on a mean streak. He's been drinking a lot lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.41,0:04:32.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定要想法出来  你绝不敢相信这件事\N{\fs14}You got to, man. Sincerely, you won't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.15,0:04:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你呢  戈帝?  -大概可以吧\N{\fs14}- Can you, Gordie? - Yeah, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.35,0:04:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事大不了的事让你像屁股着火似的紧张  维恩?\N{\fs14}So what are you pissing and moaning about, Verno?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看牌\N{\fs14}I knock.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.09,0:04:41.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少来  你又没有王牌\N{\fs14}What? You liar. You ain't got no pat hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.19,0:04:43.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才没有王牌\N{\fs14}You didn't deal yourself no pat hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.53,0:04:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别不认帐  屎蛋\N{\fs14}Make your draw, shitheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.16,0:04:49.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们想不想看死人?\N{\fs14}You guys wanna go see a dead body?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:55.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是在地板下挖宝的时候听到这件事的  明白吗?\N{\fs14}I was under the porch digging, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.91,0:04:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们立刻明白了维恩的意思\N{\fs14}We all understood what Vern meant right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.81,0:05:00.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学年刚开始的时候\N{\fs14}At the beginning of the school year...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.78,0:05:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他把钱存在钱筒  埋在他家的屋子下\N{\fs14}he had buried a quart jar of pennies underneath his house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:07.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他曾划了张藏宝图  以便日后再挖出来\N{\fs14}He drew a treasure map so he could find them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.18,0:05:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不料一个星期后  他妈整理房间时把那张图丢了\N{\fs14}A week later, his mom cleaned out his room and threw away the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维恩花了九个月的时间  在屋子下东挖西掘\N{\fs14}Vern had been trying to find those pennies for nine months.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:16.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九个月耶\N{\fs14}Nine months, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真让人哭笑不得\N{\fs14}You didn't know whether to laugh or cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老天  比利  我们一定要想想办法\N{\fs14}Jesus Christ, Billy, we gotta do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.90,0:05:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么?  谁会管这件事?\N{\fs14}Why? Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.73,0:05:27.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-但我们看见他  -又怎样?  不关我们的事\N{\fs14}- We saw him. - So? It ain't nothin' to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.57,0:05:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小鬼已经死了  也无法再让他复活\N{\fs14}The kid's dead, so it ain't nothin' to him neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁在乎是不是有人发现他  我才不管\N{\fs14}Who gives a shit if they ever find him? I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:36.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是收音机常提到那孩子的事\N{\fs14}But it's that kid they were talking about on the radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.45,0:05:39.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他好像叫布罗克  还是布罗尔或佛罗尔\N{\fs14}Brocker, or Brower, or Flowers or whatever his name is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一定是被火车撞死的\N{\fs14}The train must have hit him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么大不了的\N{\fs14}Big fuckin' deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.56,0:05:48.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们对雷·布罗尔的事很注意\N{\fs14}We had all followed the Ray Brower story very closely...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.46,0:05:50.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他和我们同龄\N{\fs14}because he was a kid our age.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.19,0:05:53.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三天前他出门采蓝莓  此后即失去踪影\N{\fs14}Three days before, he had gone out to pick blueberries and nobody had seen him since.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我们应该报警\N{\fs14}I think we should tell the cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.77,0:05:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们偷了车你还敢去招惹警察  你这白痴\N{\fs14}You don't go squawkin' to the cops after you boosted a car, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.30,0:06:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们一定会问我们  怎么去后哈洛路的\N{\fs14}They're gonna want to know how we got way out on Back Harlow Road.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们知道我们没有车子\N{\fs14}Now, they know we don't got no car.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.94,0:06:06.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们最好别泄漏这件事  这样他们就动不了我们\N{\fs14}If we just keep our mouths shut, they can't touch us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.64,0:06:09.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者我们可以打个匿名电话\N{\fs14}We could make an anonymous call.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.58,0:06:11.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会追查出来的  蠢蛋\N{\fs14}They trace those calls, stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.41,0:06:14.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在电视的警探片里看过\N{\fs14}I seen it on Highway Patrol and on Dragnet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.32,0:06:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也对\N{\fs14}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.79,0:06:18.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我们没偷那辆该死的道奇轿车就好了\N{\fs14}I just wish we had never boosted that goddamn Dodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.49,0:06:21.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果当时艾斯和我们一起  就可以说我们是坐他的车子\N{\fs14}I wish Ace had been with us. We coulda told the cops we was in his car.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-可惜他当时不在场  -要不要告诉他?\N{\fs14}- Well, he wasn't. - We gonna tell him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事我们不能告诉任何人\N{\fs14}We're not gonna tell nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.53,0:06:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不能告诉任何人\N{\fs14}Nobody, never. You dig me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.80,0:06:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道后哈洛路\N{\fs14}I know the Back Harlow Road.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.87,0:06:31.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它一直通到罗耶河边\N{\fs14}It comes to a dead end by the Royal River.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有铁路经过那里\N{\fs14}The train tracks are right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.14,0:06:36.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和我老爸  以前去过那一带钓鱼\N{\fs14}Me and my dad used to fish for cossies out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.31,0:06:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老天  要是他们知道你在下面偷听  一定会杀了你\N{\fs14}If they had known you were under there, they woulda killed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.81,0:06:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可能由柴母陵走到哈洛路吗?\N{\fs14}Could he have gotten all the way from Chamberlain to Harlow?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:43.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这段路很远\N{\fs14}That's really far.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想他一定是顺着铁道走\N{\fs14}Sure. He must've started walking on the train tracks...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.08,0:06:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样一直走到那儿\N{\fs14}and just followed them the whole way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.98,0:06:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是\N{\fs14}Yeah. Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后天黑了  一列火车疾驶而来\N{\fs14}And then, after dark, a train must've come along...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.96,0:06:54.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撞死了他\N{\fs14}and ''el smacko.''
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.52,0:06:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊\N{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:07:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了\N{\fs14}Hey, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.93,0:07:03.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我敢说如果我们先发现他  我们的照片铁定会上报\N{\fs14}I bet you that if we find him, we'll get our pictures in the paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.83,0:07:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-对  说不定还可以上电视  -当然\N{\fs14}- Yeah, we could even be on TV! - Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我们将成为英雄  -对\N{\fs14}- We'll be heroes! - Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是比利会知道  是我泄漏了这个秘密\N{\fs14}I don't know. Billy will know where I found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.91,0:07:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不会怎么样的  因为是我们发现尸体的\N{\fs14}He's not gonna care, because it's gonna be us guys that find him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.08,0:07:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比利和查理·霍根作贼心虚  也莫可奈何\N{\fs14}not Billy and Charlie Hogan in a boosted car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.35,0:07:18.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说不定会获颁勋章  维恩\N{\fs14}They'll probably pin a medal on you, Vern.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.32,0:07:20.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗?\N{\fs14}Yeah, you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.05,0:07:22.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fs14}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.09,0:07:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们该怎么跟爸爸妈妈说?\N{\fs14}What'll we tell our folks?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.45,0:07:26.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就照你刚才讲的\N{\fs14}Exactly what you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们三人说  要去你家后院露营\N{\fs14}We'll tell our folks we're tenting out in your back field...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你则说要去泰迪家过夜\N{\fs14}you tell your folks you're sleeping over at Teddy's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:34.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时告诉他们  我们明天要去参加寻宝大赛\N{\fs14}then we say we're going over to the drag races the next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.63,0:07:36.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来  我们只要在明天晚饭时回家就行了\N{\fs14}We're rock solid until tomorrow tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.47,0:07:38.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老兄  这计划真是天衣无缝\N{\fs14}Man, that's a plan and a half.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.84,0:07:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果我们真在南哈洛  发现那孩子的尸体\N{\fs14}But if we do find that kid's body over in South Harlow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.47,0:07:44.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们就会知道我们撒谎  到时恐怕会被揍扁\N{\fs14}they'll know we didn't go to the drag races, and we'll get hided.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时谁还会管这些  他们赞叹我们的大发现都来不及\N{\fs14}Nobody will care, because everybody will be so jazzed about what we found...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.98,0:07:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其它事都无关紧要了\N{\fs14}it's not gonna make a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.41,0:07:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我老爸没事照样揍我  为这被打一顿也值得\N{\fs14}My dad'll hide me anyway, but it's worth a hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-就是  -说干就干  你们怎么说?\N{\fs14}- Shit, yeah. - Let's do it. What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:07:56.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-去就去  -戈帝你呢?\N{\fs14}- All right! - Gordie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.79,0:07:58.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-当然去  -维恩?\N{\fs14}- Sure. - Vern?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:08:01.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我不知道  -维恩\N{\fs14}- I don't know. - Vern.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧  维恩\N{\fs14}Come on, Verno.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.99,0:08:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维恩\N{\fs14}Verno.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs14}Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:12.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了  好极了\N{\fs14}Too cool. Very cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:17.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望我自己能像他们一样兴奋  但就是鼓不起劲\N{\fs14}I wanted to share my friends'enthusiasm, but I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.78,0:08:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个夏天  父母几乎忘了我的存在\N{\fs14}That summer, at home, I had become the invisible boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈  你有没有看到我的水壶?\N{\fs14}Mom? Do you know where my canteen is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:31.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈!\N{\fs14}Mom
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.09,0:08:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在丹尼房里\N{\fs14}It's in Denny's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:42.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那年四月  我哥哥丹尼在车祸中丧生\N{\fs14}In April, my older brother, Dennis, had been killed in a Jeep accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,0:08:45.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过了四个月\N{\fs14}Four months had passed...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:48.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父母仍无法忘怀丧子之痛\N{\fs14}but my parents still hadn't been able to put the pieces back together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"岩城高中"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.71,0:08:59.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"密西根州立大学"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈帝  我有样东西给你\N{\fs14}Gordie, I got something for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.41,0:09:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老弟  这给你\N{\fs14}This, my friend, is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.35,0:09:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-这是你洋基球队的球帽  -它现在是你的了\N{\fs14}- This is your Yankee cap. - No, this is your Yankee cap.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是顶幸运帽  你猜戴了它  我们可以钓到多少鱼?\N{\fs14}It's a lucky cap. If you wear it, you know how many fish we'll catch?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-多少?  -成千上万\N{\fs14}- How much? - A bazillion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.16,0:09:47.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不盖你  而且你戴它很好看  简直帅毙了\N{\fs14}A bazillion fish. It looks good on you just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-妈呀  怎么黑黑的  -少调皮了  小猪\N{\fs14}- Hey, Moe, I'm going blind! - Don't start with me, porcupine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.97,0:09:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来让你老哥抱一下\N{\fs14}Come here. Give me a hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.17,0:09:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找到了\N{\fs14}You found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.14,0:09:58.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找到了\N{\fs14}You found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:00.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.38,0:10:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你不能像丹尼一样  交些好的朋友?\N{\fs14}Why can't you have friends like Denny's?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.35,0:10:11.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们也没什么不好\N{\fs14}Dad, they're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:14.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才怪  一个是小偷  另外两个是傻瓜\N{\fs14}Sure they are. A thief and two feebs?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.72,0:10:16.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克利斯并不是小偷\N{\fs14}Chris isn't a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.36,0:10:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他偷了学校的牛奶钱\N{\fs14}He stole the milk money at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是小偷是什么?\N{\fs14}He's a thief in my book.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.98,0:10:41.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们出发找雷·布罗尔的尸体时\N{\fs14}It was almost noon as we set out...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.72,0:10:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经快中午了\N{\fs14}to find the body of a dead kid named Ray Brower.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:45.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在这里让我下\N{\fs14}Right here's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.52,0:10:48.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨  克利斯\N{\fs14}Hey, Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-谢了  -小事情\N{\fs14}- Thanks a lot. - Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:53.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-戈帝  -嗨  老兄\N{\fs14}- Gordo. - Hey, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.70,0:10:57.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-想不想看好东西?  -好啊  什么?\N{\fs14}- Wanna see something? - Sure. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.07,0:10:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你还好吧?  -没什么\N{\fs14}- You okay? - Yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.97,0:11:00.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-来啊  -到底是什么?\N{\fs14}- Come on. - What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:03.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你一定得看看这玩意儿  -好了  快说是什么?\N{\fs14}- You gotta see this. - Come on, man. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.24,0:11:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快告诉我是什么?\N{\fs14}Come on. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.08,0:11:17.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想当独行侠还是大镖客?\N{\fs14}You wanna be the Lone Ranger or the Cisco Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太酷了  我的天啊\N{\fs14}Walkin', talkin'Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.12,0:11:21.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你哪儿弄来的?\N{\fs14}Where'd you get this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.96,0:11:23.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从我老头的衣柜里摸出来的\N{\fs14}Hawked it from my old man's bureau.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.76,0:11:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-这是45口径手枪  -我看的出来\N{\fs14}- It's a .45. - I can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:33.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-有没有子弹?  -有啊\N{\fs14}- You got shells for it? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.37,0:11:35.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把盒子里所有子弹都带来了\N{\fs14}I took all that was left in the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.44,0:11:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爸会以为他喝醉时  射啤酒罐用光了\N{\fs14}My dad'll think he used them himself shooting at beer cans when he was drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.78,0:11:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-里面装了子弹吗?  -当然没有  你以为我那么笨?\N{\fs14}- Is it loaded? - Hell, no. What do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老天\N{\fs14}Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.82,0:11:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快离开这里\N{\fs14}Let's get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.82,0:11:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是戈帝干的  戈帝·吕强斯想扫平岩城\N{\fs14}Gordie did it! Gordie Lachance is shooting up Castle Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:58.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么人?  谁在这里放炮?\N{\fs14}Who did that? Who's letting cherry bombs off out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真该看看刚才自己的表情\N{\fs14}Man, you should've seen your face. Damn, that was cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:07.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他妈的绝死了  -你知道那枪装了子弹  浑球\N{\fs14}- That was really fine. - You knew it was loaded, you wet end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.67,0:12:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会完蛋  刚才塔波太太看到我了\N{\fs14}I'm gonna be in trouble. That Tupper babe saw me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.84,0:12:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少来了  她以为我们是在放鞭炮\N{\fs14}Shit, she thought it was firecrackers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.64,0:12:14.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我不管  你不该这样耍我  -戈帝\N{\fs14}- I don't care. That was a mean trick. - Hey, Gordie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.01,0:12:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道有子弹\N{\fs14}I didn't know it was loaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.45,0:12:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不骗你  -你敢发誓吗?\N{\fs14}- Honest. - You swear?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.02,0:12:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  我发誓\N{\fs14}Yeah, I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.99,0:12:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以你妈妈的名誉发誓?\N{\fs14}On your mother's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.75,0:12:25.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以\N{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:27.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你撒谎她得下地狱  你敢吗?\N{\fs14}Even if she goes to hell 'cause you lied?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.89,0:12:29.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以此发誓\N{\fs14}Yeah, I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.79,0:12:32.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一言既出\N{\fs14}Pinky swear?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.46,0:12:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驷马难追\N{\fs14}Pinky swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:45.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-小妹妹  上哪儿去?  -拿来  那是我哥给我的\N{\fs14}- Hey, girls, where you going? - Come on, my brother gave me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.94,0:12:48.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-现在你送给我了  -快还给我!\N{\fs14}- And now you're giving it to me. - Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样  那是我的\N{\fs14}Come on, man. That's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是个大浑球\N{\fs14}You're a real asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.89,0:13:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大眼  你老弟真没礼貌\N{\fs14}Your brother's not very polite, Eyeball.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.29,0:13:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克利斯多佛\N{\fs14}Now, Christopher...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:04.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你不是有意得罪我朋友\N{\fs14}I know you didn't mean to insult my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.39,0:13:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道他不是有意的\N{\fs14}I know he didn't mean to insult me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此我愿给他个机会  收回那句话\N{\fs14}That's why I'm gonna give him the opportunity of taking it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他妈的  -收回那句话  小鬼\N{\fs14}- Shit. - Take it back, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.54,0:13:18.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样  快住手  你会打伤他的\N{\fs14}Stop it. You're hurting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-王八蛋  放开我  -快住手  别再打了\N{\fs14}- You bastard. Let go, man. - Stop it, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.44,0:13:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那句话收回去\N{\fs14}Take it back, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:24.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手\N{\fs14}Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.45,0:13:27.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  我收回那句话\N{\fs14}Okay, I take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.05,0:13:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才对\N{\fs14}There.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:35.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得好多了\N{\fs14}Now I feel a whole lot better about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.53,0:13:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢?\N{\fs14}How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.26,0:13:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.13,0:13:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待会儿见  小妹妹\N{\fs14}See you later, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:13:59.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  忘了这件事\N{\fs14}Come on. Just forget 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.96,0:14:15.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们带那把枪有什么用?\N{\fs14}What do we need a pistol for, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.26,0:14:17.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上在森林中过夜很恐怖\N{\fs14}It's spooky sleeping out at night in the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说不定会遇见狗熊\N{\fs14}We might see a bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.97,0:14:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可能撞到垃圾桶\N{\fs14}Or a garbage can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.47,0:14:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我带了把梳子  -你带梳子有何用?\N{\fs14}- I brought a comb. - What do we need a comb for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们要上电视  可以打扮的好看一点  是吧?\N{\fs14}If we get on TV, we want to look good, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.85,0:14:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你想的真周到  维恩  -不敢当\N{\fs14}- That's a lot of thinking, Vern. - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.45,0:14:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赏你两拳当奖品\N{\fs14}Two for flinching.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.22,0:14:41.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想大概得走多远?\N{\fs14}How far do you think it's gonna be?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.03,0:14:45.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果一直顺着铁道走到哈洛\N{\fs14}If we follow the tracks all the way into Harlow...
