Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.79,0:22:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有别的什么  而当时的我们都有同感\N{\fs14}there was more, and that we all knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.26,0:22:32.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们应有尽有\N{\fs14}Everything was there and around us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.53,0:22:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现了真正的自己\N{\fs14}We knew exactly who we were...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.16,0:22:36.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且知道自己要做什么\N{\fs14}and exactly where we were going.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.93,0:22:38.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种感觉很棒\N{\fs14}It was grand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.17,0:22:45.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真了不起  光会欺负胖小孩  真棒\N{\fs14}Great. Spit at the fat kid. Real good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.31,0:22:46.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几点了  戈帝?\N{\fs14}What time is it, Gordie?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.64,0:22:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点十五分\N{\fs14}It's 1 :1 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.01,0:22:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好赶快去买吃的  垃圾场三点就开门\N{\fs14}We better go get the food. Junkyard opens at 3:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.05,0:22:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丑巴到时候也会来\N{\fs14}Chopper will be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.78,0:22:56.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咬命根子\N{\fs14}Sic balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.29,0:22:59.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去吧  然后在回来的路口会合我们\N{\fs14}You go. You can pick us up on the way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.79,0:23:01.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不一个人去  要就大伙一起去\N{\fs14}I'm not going alone. We should all go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.66,0:23:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要留在这里\N{\fs14}I'm staying right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.13,0:23:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不去\N{\fs14}Yeah, man, I'm not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.46,0:23:08.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  女孩们  别吵  我们丢铜板决定\N{\fs14}Girls, girls, girls, cool it. We'll flip for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.50,0:23:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.73,0:23:11.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一不一样的人去\N{\fs14}Odd man goes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.23,0:23:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是你  戈帝  你这怪胎\N{\fs14}That's you, Gordie. Odd as a cod.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.17,0:23:14.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快丢  少说废话\N{\fs14}Flip or eat lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.88,0:23:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全是反面\N{\fs14}Four tails!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.41,0:23:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老天  这是个坏预兆\N{\fs14}Oh,Jesus, that's a goocher.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.75,0:23:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这并不代表任何意义\N{\fs14}That doesn't mean anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.65,0:23:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我们再丢一次  -真的\N{\fs14}- Let's go again. - No, man, a goocher.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.72,0:23:30.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这预兆代表恶运\N{\fs14}That's really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.29,0:23:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们还记得  克林·布拉肯那帮人\N{\fs14}You remember when Clint Bracken and those guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.22,0:23:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被干的事吗?\N{\fs14}got wiped out on Weed Hill in Durham?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.19,0:23:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比利说  他们当时以丢铜板赌啤酒\N{\fs14}Billy told me they were flippin' for beers...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.86,0:23:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在离开酒吧前  他们也丢了个全是反面的凶兆\N{\fs14}and they came up with a goocher just before they got into the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.10,0:23:42.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果砰的一声  他们全被炸得血肉横飞\N{\fs14}And bang! They all got totalled!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.93,0:23:45.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的不喜欢这种兆头\N{\fs14}I don't like this. Sincerely.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.67,0:23:46.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维恩\N{\fs14}Verno...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.00,0:23:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人相信这种胡说八道的鬼话\N{\fs14}nobody believes that crap about moons and goochers. It's baby stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.71,0:23:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再丢一次\N{\fs14}Now flip again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.71,0:23:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底丢不丢?\N{\fs14}Are you gonna flip or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.71,0:23:59.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  维恩  我们不能耗一整天\N{\fs14}Come on, Vern. We don't have all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.79,0:24:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你输了  戈帝\N{\fs14}You lose, Gordie.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.72,0:24:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈帝输了  戈帝老兄一定是昨晚做了坏事\N{\fs14}Gordie loses. Gordie just screwed the pooch.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.59,0:24:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道"白痴"是什么意思吗?\N{\fs14}Does the word ''retarded'' mean anything to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.13,0:24:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈帝  快去买东西吧  你这贱货\N{\fs14}Go get the provisions, you morphadite.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.73,0:24:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要用你妈的小名叫我\N{\fs14}Don't call me any of your mother's pet names.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.20,0:24:21.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真像个大姑娘似的\N{\fs14}What a wet end you are, Lachance.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.74,0:24:24.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-闭嘴  -我不闭嘴\N{\fs14}- Shut up. - I don't shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.31,0:24:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我越长越大  每次看到你  仍忍不住张大嘴  想吐\N{\fs14}I grow up, and when I look at you, I throw up.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.28,0:24:31.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你妈会走到墙角  把地上舔得一干二净\N{\fs14}And then your mother goes around the corner and she licks it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.08,0:24:37.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能找出恶心低级的新字眼  来调侃朋友的母亲\N{\fs14}Finding new, and preferably disgusting, ways to degrade a friend's mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.99,0:24:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我们是件很有面子的事\N{\fs14}was always held in high regard.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.92,0:24:44.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"奎塔西路加油站"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.27,0:24:56.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是丹尼·蓝强的弟弟吗?\N{\fs14}Ain't you Denny Lachance's brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.17,0:24:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  先生\N{\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.21,0:25:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他发生意外真是可惜\N{\fs14}Shame what happened to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.08,0:25:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣经上说"生命中  常笼罩着死亡的阴影"\N{\fs14}Bible says, ''In the midst of life, we are in death.''
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.58,0:25:07.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听过吗?\N{\fs14}Did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.02,0:25:11.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有一个弟弟在韩国战死\N{\fs14}I lost a brother in Korea.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.02,0:25:16.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你长得挺像丹尼  有人告诉过你吗?\N{\fs14}You look like your brother. People ever tell you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.49,0:25:19.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有几次\N{\fs14}Sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.00,0:25:24.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还记得那年他打过全国联赛\N{\fs14}I remember the year he was all-conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.30,0:25:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他担任四分卫\N{\fs14}Quarterback, he played.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.57,0:25:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他传起球来真有一手\N{\fs14}Boy, could he throw.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.20,0:25:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣父  圣子和圣灵\N{\fs14}Father, God, and SonnyJesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.31,0:25:39.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天的球赛  可能有些球探会到场\N{\fs14}Could be some scouts at the game tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.38,0:25:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-很难说  爸  -可不可以把马铃薯给我?\N{\fs14}- I don't know, Pop. - Dad, can I have the potatoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.52,0:25:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-听说球探一定会来  儿子  -你打完球是否要和珍妮见面\N{\fs14}- That's what I hear, son. - Are you gonna seeJane after the game?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.95,0:25:47.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是个很可爱的女孩\N{\fs14}I think she's a lovely girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.86,0:25:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-麻烦把马铃薯给我好吗?  -桃乐兰  别跟他谈女孩子的事\N{\fs14}- Dad, can I please have the potatoes? - Dorothy, don't talk to the boy about girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.99,0:25:55.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这时他应该心无杂念  这是他生命中最重要的一场比赛\N{\fs14}He shouldn't be thinking about girls. This is the biggest game of his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.30,0:25:58.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丹尼  你明天比赛的时候\N{\fs14}Dennis, when you're out there tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.70,0:26:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸  你有没有看到  戈帝写的那篇文章?\N{\fs14}Did you read the story Gordie wrote? Gordie wrote a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.97,0:26:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-写得真的很好  -你写了些什么  宝贝?\N{\fs14}- It was really good. - What did you write, sweetheart?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.87,0:26:08.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  我说得不错吧  踢足球一定要集中精神\N{\fs14}See? That's what I'm talking about. Football takes concentration.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.84,0:26:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你却跟他提女友的事  害他心不在焉\N{\fs14}You start in on the girls, and his mind's all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.98,0:26:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈帝  我喜欢那篇文章  我觉得你写得很棒\N{\fs14}Gordie, I really liked it. I thought it was great.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.49,0:26:23.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也会玩足球吗?\N{\fs14}You play football?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.39,0:26:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你也会玩足球吗?\N{\fs14}Do you play football?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.03,0:26:29.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会\N{\fs14}No
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.53,0:26:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你会什么?\N{\fs14}What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.17,0:26:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.44,0:26:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  你哥哥丹尼  足球玩得真是好\N{\fs14}Well, your brother, Denny, sure could play football.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.61,0:26:47.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看  一块半汉堡\N{\fs14}There you go, kid. Buck and a half of hamburger.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.88,0:27:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼  你们在那里做什么?  给我过来\N{\fs14}Hey, you kid. What are you doing there? Come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.48,0:27:20.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来这里\N{\fs14}You! Come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.42,0:27:23.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他妈的再不回来  我就放狗咬你们\N{\fs14}Come back here, goddammit! I'll sic my dog on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.15,0:27:24.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑  戈帝\N{\fs14}Run, Gordie!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.95,0:27:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丑巴  咬他  咬那孩子\N{\fs14}Chopper, sic him! Sic him, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.42,0:27:30.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说的是"咬那孩子"\N{\fs14}Now, he said "Sic him, boy. "
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.49,0:27:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我听成了  "丑巴  咬他命根子"\N{\fs14}But what I heard was, "Chopper, sic balls. "
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.08,0:27:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是丑巴?\N{\fs14}That's Chopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.41,0:27:52.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看见丑巴使我第一次\N{\fs14}Chopper was my first lesson...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.58,0:27:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解到传言和事实的差距那么大\N{\fs14}in the vast difference between myth and reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.35,0:27:58.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来呀  丑屁  来亲我的屁股\N{\fs14}Come on, Choppy. Kiss my ass, Choppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.26,0:28:01.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吃屎吧  臭狗\N{\fs14}Bite shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.26,0:28:06.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来  丑屁  看你敢不敢咬我的命根子\N{\fs14}Come on, Choppy. Sic balls, Choppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.36,0:28:09.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼  别逗那只狗  听见没有\N{\fs14}You kids stop teasing that dog. You hear me? Stop teasing him!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.46,0:28:12.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小混蛋  你们再笑它  我打烂你们的屁股\N{\fs14}Sonny, I'm gonna beat your ass, teasing my dog like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.50,0:28:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就翻过墙来抓我们  大肥猪\N{\fs14}Try climbing this fence to get me, fat ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.37,0:28:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你敢这样叫我  你这个小人渣\N{\fs14}Don't you call me that, you little tin weasel.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.61,0:28:20.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是个疯子的小孩\N{\fs14}Peckerwood loony's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.78,0:28:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫我什么?\N{\fs14}What'd you call me?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.55,0:28:26.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你  你是泰迪·杜强\N{\fs14}I know who you are. You're Teddy Duchamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.85,0:28:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爸爸是个神经病\N{\fs14}Your dad's a loony.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.55,0:28:30.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他现在被关在托哥斯的疯人院里\N{\fs14}A loony up in the nuthouse at Togus.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.79,0:28:33.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他曾经把你耳朵扯到火炉边  差点烧了你的狗耳\N{\fs14}He took your ear and put it to a stove and burnt it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.12,0:28:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父亲是诺曼第登陆战的英雄\N{\fs14}My father stormed the beach at Normandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.39,0:28:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他比璗房里的老鼠还神经\N{\fs14}He's crazier than a shithouse rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.86,0:28:41.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难怪你也不大正常\N{\fs14}No wonder you're acting the way you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.90,0:28:43.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是有疯父必有疯子\N{\fs14}with a loony for a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.70,0:28:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你再说我爹是疯子  我就杀了你\N{\fs14}You call my dad a loony again and I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.50,0:28:49.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疯子!  疯子!  疯子!\N{\fs14}loony loony loony
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.14,0:28:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要拧断你的头  打断你的颈子\N{\fs14}I'm gonna rip your head off and shit down your neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.44,0:28:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要杀了他\N{\fs14}I'm gonna kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.41,0:28:57.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有种过来试试  你这讨厌的小王八蛋\N{\fs14}You come on and try it, you little slimy bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.98,0:29:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他只是想骗你过去揍你一顿  然后把你交给警察\N{\fs14}He wants you to go over there so he can beat you up and take you to the cops!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.32,0:29:04.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我闭嘴  精灵鬼  让他自己来打一架\N{\fs14}You watch your mouth, smart guy. Let him do his own fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.32,0:29:07.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你起码比他重五百磅  大肥猪\N{\fs14}You only outweigh him by 500 pounds, fat ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.42,0:29:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你的名字\N{\fs14}I know your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.62,0:29:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是蓝强家的小鬼  你们我全都认识\N{\fs14}You're Lachance. I know all you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.49,0:29:15.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等会儿  会打电话给你们的爸爸\N{\fs14}And all your fathers are gonna get a call from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.26,0:29:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了那个被关在托哥斯的疯子\N{\fs14}Except for the loony up in Togus.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.20,0:29:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要杀了你\N{\fs14}I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.17,0:29:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,满口脏舌的小烂货\N{\fs14}You little foulmouthed whoremaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.04,0:29:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是婊子养的\N{\fs14}You son of a bitch. I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.51,0:29:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚回来  听到没有?\N{\fs14}Come back here. You hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.75,0:29:32.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我不准任何人侮辱我老头  -回来\N{\fs14}- Nobody ranks out my old man. - Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.41,0:29:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爸爸是诺曼第登陆的英雄\N{\fs14}My father stormed the beach at Normandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.38,0:29:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个英雄  大肥猪\N{\fs14}He stormed the beach, you faggot!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.93,0:29:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经给了他颜色看  他还以为我们好欺负\N{\fs14}We showed him. Thought we were a bunch of pussies.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.17,0:29:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他侮辱我老头\N{\fs14}He ranked my old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.24,0:29:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白泰迪为什么那么在乎他那狠心的爸爸?\N{\fs14}I wondered why Teddy cared so much for his dad, who practically killed him...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.01,0:29:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我爸我才不在乎\N{\fs14}and I couldn't give a shit about my own dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.07,0:30:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而他自我三岁后就没摸过我\N{\fs14}who hadn't laid a hand on me since I was three.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.51,0:30:03.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而那次还是为了我偷吃水槽下的洗衣粉\N{\fs14}And that was for eating bleach under the sink.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.58,0:30:05.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他侮辱我老头\N{\fs14}He ranked my old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.01,0:30:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你何必管那肥屎蛋怎么说你爸?\N{\fs14}What do you care what a fat old pile of shit like him says about your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.75,0:30:12.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爸仍然是登陆诺曼第的英雄  对吧?\N{\fs14}He still stormed the beach at Normandy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.82,0:30:14.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别提了\N{\fs14}Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.12,0:30:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道那老混球也登陆过诺曼第?\N{\fs14}You think that pile of shit was at Normandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.26,0:30:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别提了  好吧?\N{\fs14}Forget it, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.73,0:30:19.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他根本对你老头一无所知  只会乱放狗屁\N{\fs14}He don't know nothing about your old man. He's just dog shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.96,0:30:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和你爸的感情  绝不会因他而改变\N{\fs14}Whatever is between you and your old man. He can't change that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.47,0:30:25.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别提了  好吗?  别再说了\N{\fs14}Forget it, all right? Just forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.98,0:30:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身怀单枪会遍英雄好汉\N{\fs14}Have gun will travel reads the card of a man
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.12,0:30:48.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赤手空拳不畏龙潭虎穴\N{\fs14}A knight without armor in a savage land
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.60,0:30:57.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉  因为我扫了大家的兴\N{\fs14}I'm sorry if I'm spoiling everybody's good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.73,0:31:01.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么  不要这样想\N{\fs14}It's okay, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.77,0:31:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怀疑这件事会真值得高兴\N{\fs14}I'm not sure it should be a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.51,0:31:07.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想回去了?\N{\fs14}You saying you want to go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.04,0:31:09.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是\N{\fs14}No
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.74,0:31:12.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但去看一个死了的孩子\N{\fs14}But going to see a dead kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.18,0:31:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不应该像去参加舞会一样\N{\fs14}Maybe it shouldn't be a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.32,0:31:16.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对呀\N{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.55,0:31:20.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定他血肉模糊  四分五裂\N{\fs14}Like if he's all cut up and blood and shit all over him...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.89,0:31:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我一定会做恶梦  -好了  维恩\N{\fs14}- I might have nightmares. - Come on, Vern.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.69,0:31:26.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许他内脏和眼珠子  都跑了出来  他还会抓人\N{\fs14}You know, like guts and eyeballs all ready to jump and grab you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.63,0:31:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不讲话没人当你是哑巴  -我忍不住嘛\N{\fs14}- Shut up, Vern, goddamm it! - I can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.50,0:31:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fs14}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.67,0:31:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这时是两点四十五分  但感觉上已很晚\N{\fs14}It was only 2:45, but it felt much later.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.07,0:31:40.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是因为天气太热  以及出了太多意外\N{\fs14}It was too hot, and too much had happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.78,0:31:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们连罗耶河都还没看见\N{\fs14}We weren't even close to the Royal River yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.91,0:31:47.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想在天黑前多赶点路  非得加快脚步\N{\fs14}We were gonna have to get moving to make some real miles before dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.89,0:31:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"眼镜蛇"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.59,0:31:58.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动好吧\N{\fs14}Just hold still, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.23,0:32:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和那个叫康妮·巴乐摩道的小妞进展如何?\N{\fs14}So what's with you and this Connie Palermo chick?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.07,0:32:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们约会了一个月\N{\fs14}I've been seeing her for over a month now...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.20,0:32:11.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她只肯让我摸她胸部\N{\fs14}and all she'll let me do is feel her tits.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.61,0:32:15.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是个天主教徒  兄弟  他们就是这副德性\N{\fs14}She's a Catholic, man. They're all like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.21,0:32:18.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要爽一发  你要泡个基督教徒\N{\fs14}You wanna get laid, you gotta get yourself a Protestant.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.11,0:32:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犹太人也可以\N{\fs14}Jew's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.85,0:32:23.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KLAM电台新闻快报\N{\fs14}A KLAM newsbreak.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.42,0:32:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在暂时中断节目\N{\fs14}We interrupt to bring you an update...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.95,0:32:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为您报导搜寻十二岁  失踪男孩雷·布罗尔最新进展\N{\fs14}on the search for the missing twelve-year-old, Ray Brower.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.82,0:32:29.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警方已扩大搜索范围\N{\fs14}The police have expanded their efforts...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.82,0:32:31.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至莫顿与德汉镇及其郊区\N{\fs14}to include Mutton, Durham, and the outlying areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.06,0:32:33.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们什么时候才死心\N{\fs14}When are they gonna give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.96,0:32:36.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小鬼死了  他们永远也找不到他\N{\fs14}The kid's gone. They're never gonna find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.13,0:32:38.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他们找错了地方  -嘿\N{\fs14}- Not where they're lookin'. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.40,0:32:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说对了吧  查理  我们绝对找不到他\N{\fs14}Eyeball's right, Charlie. They ain't never gonna find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.00,0:32:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别乱动好吗?  害我把蛇身都划歪了\N{\fs14}Would you hold still? You're makin' me fuck up the snake part.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.31,0:32:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道他们何时才会发现他\N{\fs14}I'll tell you how they're gonna find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.51,0:32:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等到十年后  有猎户进森林里尿尿时\N{\fs14}Ten years from now, some hunter's gonna go out in the woods to take a leak...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.41,0:32:52.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会发现  自己竟尿在他的骨头上\N{\fs14}and wind up pissin' on his bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.65,0:32:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我赌一千块要不了那么久  他就会被发现\N{\fs14}I bet you a thousand bucks they find him before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.95,0:32:56.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两千元赌他们找不到\N{\fs14}I'll bet you $2,000 they don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.99,0:32:59.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-既然这样  混球  -这件事有什么好赌的?\N{\fs14}- Well, asshole... - What's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.89,0:33:01.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管他们找不找得到\N{\fs14}Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.22,0:33:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个都给我闭上狗嘴\N{\fs14}Would you two just shut the fuck up?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.49,0:33:06.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你们两个混球有两千元  我早把你们给宰了\N{\fs14}If either one of you assholes had $2,000, I'd kill you both.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.96,0:33:09.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在又回到"大老板"鲍伯·克米尔主持的音乐时间\N{\fs14}We're back here with the bossman, Bob Cormier.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.03,0:33:12.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面为您介绍一首  超人气畅销曲\N{\fs14}From the racks and stacks, it's the best on wax.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.60,0:33:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯爹合唱团的"棒棒糖"\N{\fs14}It's the Cordettes, with "Lollipop. "
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.63,0:33:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有些香烟  从我老头衣柜里弄来的\N{\fs14}Hey, I got some Winstons. Hawked 'em off my old man's dresser.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.47,0:33:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-吃过晚饭可以来一根  -酷毙了\N{\fs14}- One apiece for after supper. - Yeah, that's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.20,0:33:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"饭后一根烟  快活似神仙"\N{\fs14}That's when a cigarette tastes best. After supper.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.14,0:33:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs14}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.62,0:34:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你觉得我是个怪人吗?  -不是才怪\N{\fs14}- Do you think I'm weird? - Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.95,0:34:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老兄  我是说真的  我真的很古怪吗?\N{\fs14}No, man, seriously. Am I weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.49,0:34:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  那又怎么样?  每个人都有怪的地方\N{\fs14}Yeah, but so what? Everybody's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.93,0:34:21.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-上学的事你已预备好了吗?  -好了\N{\fs14}- You ready for school? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.37,0:34:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道那代表什么?\N{\fs14}Junior high. You know what that means.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.04,0:34:28.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明年六月我们就要散了\N{\fs14}By nextJune, we'll all be split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.08,0:34:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么?  怎么会呢?\N{\fs14}What are you talking about? Why would that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.38,0:34:33.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那时  一切都和上小学不一样了\N{\fs14}It's not gonna be like grammar school, that's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.18,0:34:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要读大学先修班\N{\fs14}You'll be taking your college courses...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.25,0:34:38.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我  泰迪和维恩  得和其他白痴进就业班\N{\fs14}and me, Teddy and Vern will all be in the shop courses...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.55,0:34:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学做烟灰缸或鸟笼之类的东西\N{\fs14}with the rest of the retards making ashtrays and birdhouses.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.13,0:34:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时你会认识很多新朋友\N{\fs14}You're gonna meet a lot of new guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.03,0:34:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是聪明人\N{\fs14}Smart guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.53,0:34:49.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的意思是认识一堆拙蛋\N{\fs14}Meet a lot of pussies is what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.50,0:34:52.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要这样说  老兄  也千万别那样想\N{\fs14}No, man. Don't say that. Don't even think that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.53,0:34:55.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会去和那些驴蛋混在一起的  别想\N{\fs14}I'm not going in with a lot of pussies. Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.20,0:34:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你就是个混蛋\N{\fs14}Then you're an asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.64,0:34:58.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想和你们当朋友算是混蛋?\N{\fs14}What's asshole about wanting to be with your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.71,0:35:00.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和害你堕落的人来往就是混球\N{\fs14}It's asshole if your friends drag you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.94,0:35:04.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我们在一起  你只会变成一个满脑子浆糊的老油条\N{\fs14}You hang with us, you'll just be another wise guy with shit for brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.25,0:35:07.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想太空飞鼠打得赢超人吗?\N{\fs14}You think Mighty Mouse could beat up Superman?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.72,0:35:10.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你是不是头脑有问题?  -为什么不行?\N{\fs14}- What are you? Cracked? - Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.39,0:35:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一天他一只手举起五只大象\N{\fs14}I saw the other day, he was carrying five elephants in one hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.49,0:35:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老天  你真不是普通的笨\N{\fs14}Boy, you don't know nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.56,0:35:19.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太空飞鼠只是卡通人物  超人则是真正的人\N{\fs14}Mighty Mouse is a cartoon. Superman is a real guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.19,0:35:21.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡通里的人  怎么可能打得赢真人?\N{\fs14}No way a cartoon could beat up a real guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.86,0:35:25.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许你说得有道理\N{\fs14}Yeah, maybe you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.83,0:35:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是他们打起来一定很精彩\N{\fs14}It would be a good fight, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.04,0:35:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一天  你也许会成为作家  戈帝\N{\fs14}You could be a real writer someday, Gordie.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.14,0:35:35.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去他的写作  我才不要当什么鬼作家\N{\fs14}Fuck writing. I don't want to be a writer.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.88,0:35:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢人才当作家  才把时间浪费在写文章\N{\fs14}It's stupid. It's a stupid waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.15,0:35:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-那全是你爸的口气  -胡扯\N{\fs14}- That's your dad talking. - Bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.22,0:35:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才怪  我知道你爸根本不管你\N{\fs14}Bulltrue. I know how your dad doesn't give a shit about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.15,0:35:47.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一向只关心丹尼  别告诉我我说错了\N{\fs14}Denny was the one he cared about, and don't try to tell me different.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.16,0:35:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还只是个孩子  戈帝\N{\fs14}You're just a kid, Gordie.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.90,0:35:57.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗?  谢谢你  老爹\N{\fs14}Gee, thanks, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.83,0:36:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒真希望我是你爸爸\N{\fs14}I wish to hell I was your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.47,0:36:06.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样你就不至于  有想上就业班的蠢念头\N{\fs14}You wouldn't be going around...talking about taking these stupid shop courses if I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.01,0:36:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上帝赐予你珍贵的礼物\N{\fs14}It's like God gave you something, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.28,0:36:11.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你编的那些故事\N{\fs14}All those stories that you can make up...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.41,0:36:14.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一定希望你珍惜这能力  不要糟蹋了它\N{\fs14}and He said, ''This is what we got for you, kid, try not to lose it.''
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.75,0:36:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但除非有人好好看顾小孩子常会糟蹋东西\N{\fs14}But kids lose everything unless there's someone there to look out for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.22,0:36:21.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你父母搞杂了  也许真该由我来盯着你\N{\fs14}And if your parents are too fucked up to do it, then maybe I should.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.96,0:36:24.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两位老兄  快点\N{\fs14}Come on, you guys. Let's get moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.03,0:36:28.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不快点  等我们到那里  那小鬼说不定又活过来了\N{\fs14}By the time we get there, the kid won't be dead anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.44,0:37:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们知不知道  下一班火车什么时候来?\N{\fs14}Any of you guys know when the next train is due?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.71,0:37:20.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以走  136号公路的桥过河\N{\fs14}We could go down to the Route 1 36 bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.22,0:37:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你疯了?  我们得顺着河  走五英里才能到那座桥\N{\fs14}What are you, crazy? That's five miles down the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.45,0:37:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我们又得顺着河  走五英里路回到铁路\N{\fs14}You walk five miles down the river, you gotta walk five miles back.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.55,0:37:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定得走到天黑\N{\fs14}That could take till dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.49,0:37:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说我们就由这里过河  不到十分钟就可以到对岸\N{\fs14}We go across here, we could get to the same place in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.56,0:37:34.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是如果火车来了  我们就无路可走了\N{\fs14}But if a train comes, there's nowheres to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.00,0:37:38.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-谁说没有  可以跳下去  -泰迪  这桥有一百英尺高\N{\fs14}- The hell there isn't. You just jump. - Teddy, it's a hundred feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.67,0:37:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  泰迪\N{\fs14}Yeah, Teddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.87,0:37:42.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们如果想绕远路  请便\N{\fs14}You guys can go around if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.50,0:37:44.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要由这里过河\N{\fs14}I'm crossing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.41,0:37:49.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你们拖着大屁股  绕完半个地球回来时\N{\fs14}While you guys are dragging your asses halfway across the state and back...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.24,0:37:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早已在对岸等着\N{\fs14}I'll be waiting for you on the other side...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.71,0:37:54.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陷入我的一片思绪中\N{\fs14}relaxing with my thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.52,0:37:56.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沉思时  打算用左手或右手托腮?\N{\fs14}Do you use your left hand or your right hand for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.15,0:38:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你等着看好了\N{\fs14}You wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.85,0:39:07.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的梳子掉了\N{\fs14}I lost the comb.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.52,0:39:10.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  维恩\N{\fs14}Forget it, Vern.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.06,0:39:48.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火车来了\N{\fs14}Train!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.10,0:39:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真倒霉\N{\fs14}Oh, shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.74,0:39:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点走  泰迪  快点\N{\fs14}Move it, man. Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.97,0:39:59.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起来  维恩  他妈的\N{\fs14}Get up, Vern! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.24,0:40:02.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起来  快走\N{\fs14}Get up! Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.71,0:40:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他妈的  维恩  站起来\N{\fs14}Shit, Vern, get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.65,0:40:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-快点  维恩  -不行  我们会掉下去\N{\fs14}- Come on, Vern! - I don't wanna. We're gonna fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.38,0:40:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会被撞死  起来\N{\fs14}We're gonna die, damn it! Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.92,0:40:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑\N{\fs14}Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.86,0:40:19.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑\N{\fs14}Go, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.23,0:40:23.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-跑快一点  -我办不到  戈帝\N{\fs14}- Damn it, Vern, go faster! - I can't, Gordie.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.04,0:40:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑  戈帝  跑快点  加油\N{\fs14}Run, man! Move your ass, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.58,0:40:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油  维恩\N{\fs14}Come on, Vern! Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.55,0:40:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑\N{\fs14}Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.02,0:40:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油\N{\fs14}Run, man! Move your ass, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.98,0:41:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我们知道  火车什么时候会来了\N{\fs14}At least now we know when the next train was due.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.49,0:41:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是前所未见的闪火车表演  真不是盖的\N{\fs14}Man, that was the all-time train dodge. Too cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.79,0:41:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维恩  你刚才吓得\N{\fs14}Vern, you was so scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.90,0:41:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像亚柏特那胖子  看见木乃伊的表情一样\N{\fs14}you looked like that fat guy, Abbott Costello, when he saw the Mummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.97,0:41:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没有那么害怕\N{\fs14}I wasn't that scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.20,0:41:35.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维恩!\N{\fs14}Vern
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.44,0:41:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的  我没有  不骗你们\N{\fs14}No, really, I wasn't. Sincerely.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.64,0:41:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你让我们检查裤裆  看有没有吓出尿来\N{\fs14}Then you won't mind if we check your Jockeys for Hershey squirts?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.91,0:41:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去你的\N{\fs14}Go screw.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.44,0:41:44.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维恩  你最好把汉堡翻个面\N{\fs14}Vern, you better turn yours over.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.28,0:41:47.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我喜欢烤焦一点  -随你\N{\fs14}- This is the way I like to do it. - Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.08,0:41:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了  还有吗  戈帝?\N{\fs14}Oh, man. You got any more, Gordie?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.42,0:41:51.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有了  维恩\N{\fs14}Sorry, Vern.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.95,0:41:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点也不好笑  这下我要吃什么?\N{\fs14}It's not funny. What am I supposed to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.29,0:41:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你为什么不烤了老二吃?  -虽小但也算一餐\N{\fs14}- Why don't you cook your dick? - Be a small meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.30,0:42:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些王八蛋  我捡回来了\N{\fs14}Screw you guys. I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.38,0:42:21.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饭后一根烟  快乐似神仙\N{\fs14}Nothing like a smoke after a meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.18,0:42:24.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  我热爱这些时光\N{\fs14}Yeah. I cherish these moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.86,0:42:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?  我说了什么?\N{\fs14}What? What did I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.40,0:42:37.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈帝  说个故事听听好不好?\N{\fs14}Hey, Gordo, why don't you tell us a story?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.40,0:42:38.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛\N{\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.97,0:42:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-好嘛  -好嘛  戈帝\N{\fs14}- Come on. - Yeah, come on, Gordo.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.47,0:42:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是千万别说鬼故事\N{\fs14}Not one of your horror stories, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.67,0:42:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在不想听鬼故事\N{\fs14}I don't wanna hear no horror stories. I'm not up for that, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.51,0:42:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说个关于史帝尔士官  和他勇猛的陆战队弟兄的故事\N{\fs14}Why don't you tell us about Sergeant Steel and his battling leathernecks?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.08,0:42:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想说的故事  和以前的不大一样\N{\fs14}The one I've been thinking about is kind of different.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.32,0:42:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它的主题是吃派大赛\N{\fs14}It's about this pie-eating contest...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.42,0:43:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主角是个人见人厌的胖小孩  叫大卫·霍根\N{\fs14}and the main guy of the story is this fat kid nobody likes named Davie Hogan.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.86,0:43:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是查理·霍根的弟弟  如果他有个弟弟\N{\fs14}Like Charlie Hogan's brother, if he had one.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.89,0:43:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真聪明  维恩\N{\fs14}Good, Vern.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.23,0:43:08.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说下去  戈帝\N{\fs14}Go on, Gordie.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.33,0:43:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个胖孩子年纪和我们差不多  但他很胖\N{\fs14}This kid is our age, but he's fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.20,0:43:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常胖\N{\fs14}Real fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.93,0:43:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的体重将近180磅  但这不是他的错\N{\fs14}He weighs close to 1 80, but it's not his fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.54,0:43:17.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他的内分泌不正常\N{\fs14}It's his glands.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.51,0:43:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的表姐就是这样  不骗你们\N{\fs14}My cousin's like that. Sincerely.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.87,0:43:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的体重超过三百磅\N{\fs14}She weighs over 300 pounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.94,0:43:24.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是因为  内分泌腺失调之类的毛病\N{\fs14}It's supposed to be a hyboid gland or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.95,0:43:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道什么是内分泌  但她的吨位真是惊人\N{\fs14}I don't know about any hyboid gland, but what a blimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.02,0:43:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不盖你们  她看起来  就像只感恩节火鸡  有一次\N{\fs14}No shit. She looks like a Thanksgiving turkey. This one time...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.09,0:43:33.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴  维恩\N{\fs14}Shut up, Vern.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.02,0:43:36.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  说下去  戈帝  这是个好故事\N{\fs14}Yeah, right. Go on, Gordie. It's a swell story.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.06,0:43:41.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别的孩子都不叫他大卫  而称呼他"猪臀"\N{\fs14}All the kids, instead of calling him Davie, they call him '' Lard Ass.''
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.20,0:43:42.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猪臀霍根\N{\fs14}Lard Ass Hogan.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.86,0:43:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连他的弟弟妹妹们也这么叫他\N{\fs14}Even his little brother and sister call him Lard Ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.97,0:43:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而在学校  同学们又给他  取了个外号叫"欧罗肥"\N{\fs14}At school, they put this sticker on his back that says ''wide load''...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.30,0:43:53.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一逮到机会就打他骂他\N{\fs14}and they rank him out and beat him up whenever they get a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.91,0:43:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一天他心中突然灵光一闪\N{\fs14}But one day he gets an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.51,0:44:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想出了一个  小孩能想出的\N{\fs14}The greatest revenge idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.31,0:44:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最伟大报复方法\N{\fs14}a kid ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.55,0:44:06.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这玩意儿开了吗?  听不到的话请举手\N{\fs14}Is this thing on? Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.32,0:44:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在介绍参加本届\N{\fs14}Now, the next contestant...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.06,0:44:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三县吃派大赛的下一位选手\N{\fs14}in the Great TriCounty Pie Eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.16,0:44:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"校长"约翰·卫根斯\N{\fs14}Principal John Wiggins.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.94,0:44:24.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有我们的明星选手\N{\fs14}And our celebrity contestant...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.51,0:44:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来自波特兰KLAM电台的\N{\fs14}from KLAM in Portland...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.31,0:44:30.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"大老板"本人  鲍伯·克米尔\N{\fs14}the bossman himself, Bob Cormier.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.18,0:44:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有满箱满柜的最畅销唱片\N{\fs14}From the racks and stacks, it's the best on wax.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.25,0:44:39.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波特兰KLAM电台\N{\fs14}How about another golden oldie twin spin...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.69,0:44:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再放一首往日金曲如何?\N{\fs14}from KLAM in Portland?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.66,0:44:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-这简直  -太酷了\N{\fs14}- It's... - Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.46,0:44:50.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来  一位吃派新秀\N{\fs14}Next, a newcomer to the Pie Eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.43,0:44:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们十分期待他未来的成就\N{\fs14}but one we expect great things from in the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.97,0:44:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"少年大师"大卫·霍根\N{\fs14}young Master David Hogan.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.91,0:45:02.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧  小伙子?\N{\fs14}Are you all right, young man?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.98,0:45:04.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"猪臀"  旅途还愉快吗?\N{\fs14}Lard Ass, how was your trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.88,0:45:09.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说你胃口不小  "猪臀"\N{\fs14}I hear you got a big appetite, Lard Ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.25,0:45:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你休想闯过我这关\N{\fs14}Don't even think about winning this.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.72,0:45:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小子  你可真够肥\N{\fs14}Boy, are you fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.09,0:45:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别理那些傻瓜  "猪臀"\N{\fs14}Don't pay any attention to those fools, Lard Ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.03,0:45:20.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说大卫\N{\fs14}David.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.64,0:45:36.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在  各位一直期待的那位\N{\fs14}And now, the one you've all been waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.64,0:45:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是蝉联四届冠军的\N{\fs14}The four-time champion...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.81,0:45:41.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的比尔·泰惠兹\N{\fs14}our own Bill Travis.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.05,0:45:49.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好  比利小子  我本人下了注十比一赌你赢\N{\fs14}Listen, I got ten riding on you myself, Billy-boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.09,0:45:53.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了吗?\N{\fs14}All right, Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.00,0:45:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请各位把手放到背后\N{\fs14}Hands behind your backs, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.93,0:45:59.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,击鼓\N{\fs14}Drumroll.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.33,0:46:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"猪臀"  用力吃啊\N{\fs14}Hey, Lard Ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.24,0:46:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"欧罗肥"  加油\N{\fs14}Chow down, wide load.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.21,0:46:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始\N{\fs14}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.55,0:46:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃完了\N{\fs14}Done.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.43,0:46:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃完了\N{\fs14}Done.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.04,0:46:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃完了\N{\fs14}Done.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.47,0:46:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想撑下去  小子  最好放慢速度\N{\fs14}You better pace yourself if you wanna hold out, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.74,0:46:43.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"猪臀"  加油\N{\fs14}Come on, Lard Ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.31,0:46:45.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"猪臀"\N{\fs14}Lard Ass! Lard Ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.38,0:46:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"猪臀"\N{\fs14}Lard Ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.92,0:46:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,观众们料想不到\N{\fs14}What the audience didn't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.99,0:47:00.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"猪臀"其实并不在乎胜负\N{\fs14}was that Lard Ass wasn't interested in winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.90,0:47:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他只想要报复\N{\fs14}What he wanted was revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.40,0:47:07.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且在上台前  他即已准备好\N{\fs14}And right before he was introduced, he'd gotten ready for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.64,0:47:14.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"蓖麻油"
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.77,0:47:40.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃完了\N{\fs14}Done.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.34,0:47:45.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃到第五客时\N{\fs14}Diving into his fifth pie...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.34,0:47:47.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"猪臀"开始想像  自己吃的不是派\N{\fs14}Lard Ass began to imagine that he wasn't eating pies.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.01,0:47:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是牛的内脏\N{\fs14}He pretended he was eating cow flops.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.88,0:47:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老鼠肉和蓝莓酱\N{\fs14}And rat guts in blueberry sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.85,0:47:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃完了\N{\fs14}Done.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.79,0:48:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渐渐地  "猪臀"的肚子开始发出响声\N{\fs14}Slowly, a sound started to build in Lard Ass's stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.99,0:48:06.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一种怪异而吓人的响声\N{\fs14}A strange and scary sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.13,0:48:09.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那声音就像大卡车  以一百英里时速疾冲而来\N{\fs14}like a log truck coming at you at a hundred miles an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.51,0:48:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然  "猪臀"张开他的嘴\N{\fs14}Suddenly Lard Ass opened his mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.52,0:48:29.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在比尔·泰惠兹察觉之前\N{\fs14}and before Bill Travis knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.42,0:48:33.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把吃下去的五个派  全吐在他的身上  沾满他全身\N{\fs14}he was covered with five pies worth of used blueberries.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.85,0:48:36.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,观众席上的女生  吓得放声大叫\N{\fs14}The women in the audience screamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.22,0:48:39.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电台主持人鲍伯·克米尔  看了泰惠兹一眼\N{\fs14}Bossman Bob Cormier took one look at Bill Travis...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.93,0:48:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吐了卫根斯校长满头满脸\N{\fs14}and barfed on Principal Wiggins.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.16,0:48:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫根斯也吐在坐他旁边的伐木工人身上\N{\fs14}Principal Wiggins barfed on the lumberjack sitting next to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.37,0:48:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葛兰迪市长  则吐在他太太的胸前\N{\fs14}Mayor Grundy barfed on his wife's tits.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.84,0:48:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但直到那些秽物的味道  传到观众席\N{\fs14}But when the smell hit the crowd...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.44,0:48:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"猪臀"的报复行动才进入高潮\N{\fs14}that's when Lard Ass's plan really started to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.18,0:48:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩们吐得男朋友满身狼籍\N{\fs14}Girlfriends barfed on boyfriends.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.11,0:49:00.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子们则全吐在父母身上  有位胖女士在皮包里大吐\N{\fs14}Kids barfed on their parents. A fat lady barfed in her purse.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.41,0:49:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,康奈利挛生兄弟  不约而同吐了对方一身\N{\fs14}The Donnelly twins barfed on each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.02,0:49:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妇女会的会员\N{\fs14}and the Women's Auxiliary barfed...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.45,0:49:07.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也吐得羚羊保育会的会员  全身都是\N{\fs14}all over the Benevolent Order of Antelopes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.79,0:49:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此时"猪臀"得意洋洋地坐在台上  欣赏自己的杰作\N{\fs14}And Lard Ass just sat back and enjoyed what he'd created.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.76,0:49:15.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千古难见的\N{\fs14}A complete and total...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.96,0:49:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呕吐大会串\N{\fs14}barfarama.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.14,0:49:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-酷毙了  -这是我听过最棒的故事\N{\fs14}- Too cool. - Man, that was just the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.11,0:49:29.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来呢?\N{\fs14}Then what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.78,0:49:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-什么后来?  -后来怎么了?\N{\fs14}- What do you mean? - I mean, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.52,0:49:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么"后来怎么了"?  这样就完了\N{\fs14}What do you mean, ''What happened?'' That's the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.75,0:49:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以这样就结束?  就算什么鸟结局?\N{\fs14}How can that be the end? What kind of an ending is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.22,0:49:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"猪臀"后来有没有怎么样?\N{\fs14}What happened to Lard Ass?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.56,0:49:44.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道\N{\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.29,0:49:47.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许跑回家  吃一大堆起士汉堡庆祝一番吧\N{\fs14}Maybe he went home and celebrated with a couple of cheeseburgers.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.49,0:49:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的结局太烂了\N{\fs14}Jesus, that ending sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.60,0:49:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么不把它改一改  改成"猪臀"跑回家\N{\fs14}Why don't you make it so that Lard Ass goes home...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.44,0:49:56.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿枪杀了他老头\N{\fs14}and he shoots his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.30,0:49:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后他到德州加入骑警队  这样的结束不错吧?\N{\fs14}Then he runs away and he joins the Texas Rangers? How about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.91,0:50:01.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.81,0:50:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是这样就完美无缺了\N{\fs14}Something good like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.84,0:50:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢这个结局  全体大呕吐的部份最精彩\N{\fs14}I liked the ending. The barfing was really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.62,0:50:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是有件事我不明白\N{\fs14}But there's one thing I didn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.72,0:50:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是"猪臀"参加比赛  要不要交报名费?\N{\fs14}Did Lard Ass have to pay to get in the contest?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.56,0:50:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不必  维恩  他们免费让他参加\N{\fs14}No, Vern. They just let him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.49,0:50:21.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好  这故事真棒\N{\fs14}Oh, great. Great story.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.96,0:50:24.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实是个好故事  戈帝  只是结局差一点\N{\fs14}It's a great story, Gordie. I just didn't like the ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.67,0:50:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维恩  收音机呢?  听听看有没有什么消息\N{\fs14}Verno, where's the radio? Let's see if we can get some sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.43,0:50:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里\N{\fs14}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.24,0:50:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一直聊到深夜\N{\fs14}We talked into the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.28,0:50:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都在聊一些在长大之前看似有意义的废话\N{\fs14}The kind of talk that seemed important until you discover girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.02,0:50:47.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  米老鼠是只老鼠  唐老鸭是只鸭子\N{\fs14}All right, Mickey's a mouse. Donald's a duck.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.29,0:50:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布鲁托则是狗  谁知道高飞是什么动物?\N{\fs14}Pluto's a dog. What's Goofy?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.39,0:50:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若我下半辈子只能吃一样东西  我会挑什么?\N{\fs14}If I could only have one food for the rest of my life?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.30,0:50:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太容易猜了  当然是猪肉\N{\fs14}That's easy. Pez.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.80,0:50:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用樱桃调味的猪肉  不用想也知道\N{\fs14}Cherry-flavored Pez. No question about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.90,0:51:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高飞是只狗  绝对是只狗\N{\fs14}Goofy's a dog. He's definitely a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.47,0:51:08.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想这猜谜游戏  一定有事先安排\N{\fs14}I knew the $64,000 Question was fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.48,0:51:11.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能有任何人那么了解歌剧的\N{\fs14}There's no way anybody could know that much about opera.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.78,0:51:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高飞不可能是狗  他戴帽子而且还开车\N{\fs14}He can't be a dog. He wears a hat and drives a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.38,0:51:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,篷车英雄真的很好看\N{\fs14}Wagon Train 's a really cool show...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.82,0:51:22.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是你们有没有发现  他们始终走不到目的地\N{\fs14}but did you ever notice that they never get anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.46,0:51:25.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是一直走个不停\N{\fs14}They just keep wagon training.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.36,0:51:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是古怪  高飞究竟是什么鬼玩意儿?\N{\fs14}God, that's weird. What the hell is Goofy?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.23,0:51:37.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人提起雷·布罗尔  但每个人其实都在想他的事\N{\fs14}Not one of us mentioned Ray Brower, but we were all thinking about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.58,0:51:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我的妈  -是布罗尔那小鬼\N{\fs14}- Oh, my God. - It's that Brower kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.95,0:51:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的鬼魂在森林里游荡\N{\fs14}His ghost is out walking in the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.19,0:51:54.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我答应绝不卖色情书刊\N{\fs14}I promise I won't hawk no more dirty books.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.09,0:51:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也绝不敢再说话不算话\N{\fs14}I promise I won't say no more bad swears.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.92,0:51:58.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保证以后会把青豆吃光\N{\fs14}I promise I'll eat all my lima beans.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.19,0:52:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胆小鬼要打两下\N{\fs14}Two for flinching.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.27,0:52:06.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么  克利斯?\N{\fs14}What is it, Chris?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.94,0:52:09.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是郊狼\N{\fs14}Maybe it's coyotes.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.60,0:52:11.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听起来像女人的尖叫声\N{\fs14}Sounds like a woman screaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.77,0:52:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是郊狼  是他的鬼魂\N{\fs14}It's not coyotes. It's his ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.11,0:52:15.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别胡说了\N{\fs14}Oh, don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.64,0:52:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰迪  坐下\N{\fs14}Hey, Teddy, sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.61,0:52:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去找它  看看他的鬼魂\N{\fs14}I'm gonna go look for it. I want to see the ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.11,0:52:22.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-别说了  -我一定要去看看\N{\fs14}- Don't say that. - I just want to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.25,0:52:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真想看看他是什么样子\N{\fs14}I just want to see what he looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.63,0:52:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我们该轮流站岗\N{\fs14}Maybe we should stand guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.66,0:52:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好主意\N{\fs14}Yeah. That's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.47,0:52:42.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把枪给我  我来站第一班\N{\fs14}Give me the gun. I'll take the first watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.15,0:52:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上十一点\N{\fs14}2300 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.15,0:53:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轮到泰迪·杜强士官长担任警戒\N{\fs14}Corporal Teddy Duchamp stands guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.32,0:53:05.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不见敌人踪迹\N{\fs14}No sign of the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.16,0:53:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堡垒安全无虑\N{\fs14}The fort is secure.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.83,0:53:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰迪  闭嘴  张大眼睛看守\N{\fs14}Shut up, Teddy, and keep your eyes peeled.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.84,0:53:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-别搞了  泰迪  -我好不容易才快睡着\N{\fs14}- Teddy, cut it out! - I'm trying to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.68,0:53:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄弟们均已安然入睡\N{\fs14}The dogfaces rested easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.35,0:53:30.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们知道有杜强士官长在\N{\fs14}in the knowledge that Corporal Teddy Duchamp...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.18,0:53:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以高枕无忧\N{\fs14}was protecting all that was dear to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.95,0:55:09.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死的应该是你  戈帝\N{\fs14}It should have been you, Gordon.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.45,0:55:13.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吗?\N{\fs14}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.96,0:55:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做梦了\N{\fs14}You were dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.30,0:55:31.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丹尼埋葬时我没有哭\N{\fs14}I didn't cry at Denny's funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.81,0:55:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很想念他  克利斯\N{\fs14}I miss him, Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.81,0:55:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很想他\N{\fs14}I really miss him.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.98,0:55:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs14}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.15,0:55:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续睡吧\N{\fs14}Go back to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.03,0:56:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许你可以和我一起  上升学班考大学\N{\fs14}Maybe you could go into the college courses with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.53,0:56:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非太阳从西边出来\N{\fs14}That'll be the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.04,0:56:37.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不行?  你头脑很好\N{\fs14}Why not? You're smart enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.87,0:56:39.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不会让我有这个机会的\N{\fs14}They won't let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.38,0:56:42.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说?\N{\fs14}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.88,0:56:47.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,镇上的人  打心眼里瞧不起我们家\N{\fs14}It's the way the people think of my family in this town, and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.81,0:56:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们也看不起我  我只是詹伯斯家的另一个坏孩子\N{\fs14}I'm just one of those low-life Chambers kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.88,0:56:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是事实\N{\fs14}That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.05,0:56:55.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实就是如此\N{\fs14}Oh, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.22,0:56:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至没人问我真的偷了牛奶钱\N{\fs14}No one even asked me if I took the milk money that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.06,0:57:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就直接把我停学三天\N{\fs14}I just got a three-day vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.07,0:57:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是你拿的?\N{\fs14}Did you take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.57,0:57:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我\N{\fs14}Yeah, I took it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.07,0:57:12.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道是我\N{\fs14}You knew I took it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.24,0:57:14.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰迪也知道是我\N{\fs14}Teddy knew I took it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.74,0:57:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都知道是我偷的\N{\fs14}Everyone knew I took it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.58,0:57:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想甚至连维恩都知道\N{\fs14}Even Vern knew it, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.92,0:57:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我会后悔又把那钱拿出来\N{\fs14}But maybe I was sorry and I tried to give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.09,0:57:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想把钱送回去?\N{\fs14}You tried to give it back?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.26,0:57:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许\N{\fs14}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.76,0:57:31.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是也许\N{\fs14}Just maybe.
