Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.58,1:16:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你至少也该学到一点你哥哥的长处\N{\fs14}You must have at least some of your brother's good sense.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.92,1:16:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有种放马过来\N{\fs14}Suck my fat one...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.92,1:16:57.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这欺善怕恶的人渣\N{\fs14}you cheap, dime-store hood.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.26,1:17:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算怎样?  难道把我们全杀了?\N{\fs14}What are you gonna do, shoot us all?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.93,1:17:07.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  艾斯\N{\fs14}No, Ace.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.43,1:17:09.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只杀你一个\N{\fs14}Just you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.94,1:17:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会找你讨回这笔帐的\N{\fs14}We're gonna get you for this.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.45,1:17:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们未必能占得到便宜\N{\fs14}Maybe you will, and maybe you won't.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.28,1:17:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会的\N{\fs14}Oh, we will.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.30,1:17:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别想我们会随随便便就算了\N{\fs14}We're not gonna forget this, if that's what you're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.64,1:17:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个仇我们一定要报  小娃娃\N{\fs14}This is big time, baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.32,1:18:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试试你的胆子有多大?\N{\fs14}''Suck my fat one''?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.19,1:18:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的胆子有多大  蓝强?\N{\fs14}Whoever told you you had a fat one, Lachance?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.66,1:18:11.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我胆大号称天下第一\N{\fs14}Biggest one in four counties.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.83,1:18:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才怪\N{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.01,1:18:30.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要不要把他带走?\N{\fs14}Are we gonna take him?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.08,1:18:32.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs14}No
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.85,1:18:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我们走了大老远才到这里  我们可以成为英雄的\N{\fs14}But we came all this way. We were supposed to be heroes.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.36,1:18:42.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不是真英雄  泰迪\N{\fs14}Not this way, Teddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.70,1:18:48.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克利斯  帮我个忙\N{\fs14}Chris, give me a hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.20,1:18:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警察后来找到了尸体\N{\fs14}Ray Brower's body was found...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.20,1:18:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们两帮人都没出风头\N{\fs14}but neither our gang nor their gang got the credit.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.71,1:18:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为最后我们觉得\N{\fs14}In the end, we decided that an anonymous phone call...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.21,1:19:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打匿名电话报警最好\N{\fs14}was the best thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.22,1:19:07.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在回家的路上\N{\fs14}We headed home.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.72,1:19:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管每个人心里  都思潮汹涌\N{\fs14}And although many thoughts raced through our minds...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.72,1:19:12.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家却都很少开口\N{\fs14}we barely spoke.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.40,1:19:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们彻夜赶路  终于在周日\N{\fs14}We walked through the night and made it back to Castle Rock...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.06,1:19:23.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早晨五点过后回到岩城  那天是工人节的前一天\N{\fs14}a little past 5:00 on Sunday morning, the day before Labor Day.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.24,1:19:27.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只离开了两天\N{\fs14}We'd only been gone two days...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.41,1:19:29.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但回来时  都觉得这个小镇变了\N{\fs14}but somehow the town seemed different...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.91,1:19:31.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得更小\N{\fs14}smaller.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.59,1:19:51.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开学时再见了\N{\fs14}Well, see you in school.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.26,1:19:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.37,1:19:57.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上中学时再见\N{\fs14}See you in junior high.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.28,1:20:12.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一分钱\N{\fs14}Penny!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.29,1:20:25.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最好在我妈把我列入十大要犯名单前回家\N{\fs14}I better get home before my mom puts me on the ten-most-wanted list.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.81,1:20:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克利斯\N{\fs14}Hey, Chris.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.18,1:20:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别放在心上  好吗?\N{\fs14}No hard feelings, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.98,1:20:40.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会的  兄弟\N{\fs14}No way, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.82,1:20:49.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快枪利眼闯过惊涛骇浪\N{\fs14}Have gun will travel reads the card of a man
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.15,1:20:54.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赤手空拳不畏龙潭虎穴\N{\fs14}A knight without armor in a savage land
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.19,1:20:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身怀单枪会遍英雄好汉\N{\fs14}His fast gun for hire
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.84,1:21:08.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来我们跟泰迪和维恩  越来越少来往\N{\fs14}As time went on, we saw less and less of Teddy and Vern...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.51,1:21:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后他们变成  只是我们生命中的过客\N{\fs14}until eventually they became just two more faces in the halls.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.51,1:21:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事是难免的\N{\fs14}It happens sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.35,1:21:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些朋友常是一闪而逝  就像路上的行人一样\N{\fs14}Friends come in and out of your life like busboys in a restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.68,1:21:21.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说维恩中学毕业不久  就结了婚\N{\fs14}I heard that Vern got married out of high school...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.19,1:21:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生了四个孩子  现在林场操作起重机\N{\fs14}had four kids and is now the forklift operator at the Arsenault Lumber Yard.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.86,1:21:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰迪一直想加入陆军\N{\fs14}Teddy tried several times to get into the army...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.19,1:21:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但因视力及听力问题  而未能如愿\N{\fs14}but his eyes and his ear kept him out.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.03,1:21:33.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说他后来坐过一阵子牢\N{\fs14}Last I'd heard, he'd spent some time in jail...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.20,1:21:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在岩城附近打零工\N{\fs14}and was now doing odd jobs around Castle Rock.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.38,1:21:47.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我永远也无法离开这个地方  是不是  戈帝?\N{\fs14}I'm never gonna get out of this town, am I, Gordie?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.21,1:21:51.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以做到任何你想做的事\N{\fs14}You can do anything you want, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.72,1:21:54.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.55,1:21:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fs14}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.06,1:22:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,握一下手\N{\fs14}Gimme some skin.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.74,1:22:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会来找你\N{\fs14}I'll see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.14,1:22:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会先去找你\N{\fs14}Not if I see you first.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.92,1:22:24.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克利斯后来终于离开了小镇\N{\fs14}Chris did get out.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.32,1:22:27.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他和我一起上大学先修班\N{\fs14}He enrolled in the college courses with me...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.09,1:22:30.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然功课很重  但他拿出那股狠劲拼命用功\N{\fs14}and although it was hard, he gutted it out, like he always did.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.76,1:22:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺利进了大学  并成为职业律师\N{\fs14}He went on to college, and eventually became a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.66,1:22:37.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上个星期  他到一家快餐店吃饭时\N{\fs14}Last week he entered a fast-food restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.60,1:22:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前面的两个男人  一言不合吵了起来\N{\fs14}Just ahead of him, two men got into an argument.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.60,1:22:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中一个还拔出了刀子\N{\fs14}One of them pulled a knife.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.60,1:22:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一向很会做和事佬的克利斯  上前劝架\N{\fs14}Chris, who had always made the best peace, tried to break it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.77,1:22:48.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果喉咙被刺了一刀\N{\fs14}He was stabbed in the throat.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.77,1:22:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当场死亡\N{\fs14}He died almost instantly.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.95,1:22:55.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"结果喉咙被刺了一刀  当场死亡"
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.88,1:22:58.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"虽然我和他已十年不见"
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.95,1:23:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我知道我会永远怀念他"
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.63,1:23:13.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸  可不可以走了?\N{\fs14}Dad, can we go now?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.13,1:23:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你准备好了吗?  -我们一个小时前就准备好了\N{\fs14}- You ready? - Yeah. We've been ready for an hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.97,1:23:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  我马上来\N{\fs14}Okay, I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.81,1:23:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他半小时前也是那么说\N{\fs14}He said that a half hour ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.48,1:23:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爸是个怪人  一写起文章就是这副德性\N{\fs14}Yeah. My dad's weird. He gets like that when he's writing.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.83,1:23:48.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我后来再也没交到"
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.80,1:23:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"像十二岁时  那帮人一样好的朋友"
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.67,1:23:58.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"也许每个人都是如此吧"
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.04,1:24:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据史帝芬金小说《尸体》改编


